Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 021—\NCaptain's responsibility{NOTE:キャプテンの座}
Comment: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:45.02,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm not quitting!{NOTE:あたしは絶対に止めない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll continue playing, even if I have to do it alone.{NOTE:一人になっても、バレーを続けるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.25,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's obviously your fault.{NOTE:明らかにあなたの失敗よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:26.68,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,This time it is captain Ayuhara's responsibility.{NOTE:今度のことは全てキャプテンの鮎原さんの成です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:28.02,Alternative,Katori,0,0,0,,Exactly, exactly.{NOTE:そうよ、そうよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.85,Alternative,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Of course, we know that training is necessary.{NOTE:それは厳しくするの結構よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:32.77,Alternative,Fukuda,0,0,0,,But there are boundaries. I mean, just look at Okei.{NOTE:でも、おケイのように成ってしまったら元も子もないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.94,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,Yeah! You're not fit to be our captain.{NOTE:そうよ。キャプテンXXXよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.24,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.66,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Why don't you forfeit as captain for now?{NOTE:一度君はキャプテンを降りてみたらどうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.37,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,I think it's for the best.{NOTE:その方がいいと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.63,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Are you serious?{NOTE:本気ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I've lost my position as captain.{NOTE:あたしはキャプテンの座を終われた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:05.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to play after all of that?{NOTE:こんな惨めな負け犬の気持ちでプレーができるって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.43,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Here goes!{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.31,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,– Okay!\N– More!{NOTE:—はい。\\N—それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:11.90,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.81,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:13.61,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.90,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,Ah, it's her again.{NOTE:あら。あの子は来てるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.07,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,She seems down.{NOTE:XXXは可笑しいだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.15,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong?{NOTE:何だか元気はないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.53,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Pay attention!{NOTE:行くわよ！それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.16,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,{NOTE:は！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:24.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah…{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.58,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.55,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.75,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,How long has she been here?{NOTE:先からいたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:38.63,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,Not sure.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.01,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it's been a while.{NOTE:ずっと元気はない見たい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.59,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's all right?{NOTE:XXXかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.97,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,It's weird how that ball wasn't received.{NOTE:あんな玉を受けられない何て変ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.05,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is weird.{NOTE:え、本当に変ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.39,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I am talking about you.{NOTE:あたしが言ってるのはあなたたちのことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.31,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,How could you not accept such a serve?{NOTE:あんなサーブを受けられない何て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.23,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,Sorry.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:09.33,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}Fujimigahama Municipal Hospital{NOTE:富士見ヶ浜市立病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:20.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'd like to visit Kudou-san.\NShe was admitted here yesterday.{NOTE:あの、昨日入院した工藤さんに面会したいんですが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.63,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it's past visiting hours.{NOTE:あら？もう面会時間は過ぎてるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Is that so…?{NOTE:そうですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:28.31,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,Please hold on. I'll try asking the nurse in charge.{NOTE:ちょっと待って。受け持ちの看護婦さんへ聞いてみるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.27,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What if…{NOTE:もし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What if the checkup results turn out bad?{NOTE:もし精密検査の結果が酷く悪かったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.53,Alternative,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, this is all your fault!{NOTE:鮎原さん。あなたですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.74,Alternative,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Keiko ended up like this because of you!{NOTE:あなたが稽古こんな目に遭ってたんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:50.20,Alternative,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,How do you intend to make up for this, Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:責任を起こったつもりなの？鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm scared. I'm scared!{NOTE:怖い。怖いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage to face Okei.{NOTE:あたしにはおケイに会う勇気がないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.96,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,I see. So it is all right for her to drop by.{NOTE:はい。じゃ、おとししてもいいのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.71,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.{NOTE:はい。どうもありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.88,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,Looks like you can go see her after all.{NOTE:さっきの方面会できるそうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.89,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.51,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,Where did she go?{NOTE:どこへ行ったんでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.56,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,Kids these days…{NOTE:これだからね今の若い子は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:19.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Flake. Coward. Good-for-nothing.{NOTE:狡い。卑怯。無責任。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.69,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No matter what I say, there's no excuse.{NOTE:何と言われても、返す言葉がないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:24.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why didn't I stay and hear the checkup results?{NOTE:なぜはっきりと検査の結果を聞けなかったのかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:だけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.49,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If the checkup results are bad…{NOTE:もし結果が悪かったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:32.33,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,…there will be no place for me to escape to.{NOTE:あたしには逃げ場がないんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Will this hand hit a volleyball ever again?{NOTE:その時はこの手がボールと別れる時…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.42,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thinking about that scares me…{NOTE:あたしはそれを知るのが恐ろしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.76,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,– Ayuhara-san.\N– Ah, Oohara-san.{NOTE:—鮎原さん。\\N—あ、大原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.34,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Why don't we play for a bit?\N– Eh?{NOTE:—あたしと練習しない？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.76,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I haven't seen your spike for quite a while now.{NOTE:久しぶりにあなたの腕が見たいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.14,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach.{NOTE:行きましょう、海へ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.89,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:54.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:57.73,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.86,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Don't be swayed by the wind!{NOTE:風に流されないように。それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:07.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I know.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—はい。\\N—あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.87,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,How could you not accept that serve, Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:あんなボールとして来ないなんてどうかしてるんじゃない、鮎原さん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.66,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You're spacing out, aren't you?{NOTE:何か考え事してるのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.42,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You're not doing yourself any good,\Npracticing in such a state.{NOTE:あなたそんな時にいくら練習しても無駄よ、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.88,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Let's call it quits.{NOTE:もう止めましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.85,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Give me the ball back.{NOTE:さ、ボール買えして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No. Let's play once more.{NOTE:いいえ。もう一度お願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:38.18,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Sorry, but there's no point.{NOTE:悪いけど、意味ないな、そんなXじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:41.98,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,If I got serious you wouldn't stand a chance.{NOTE:あたしが本気でサーブしたら、受けられないもんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can do it.{NOTE:出来ます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I think I'm better than your teammates.{NOTE:さっきの部員の方達より、あたしの方が上手いと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.32,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Those are some strong words.{NOTE:大した自身ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.45,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Are you serious about that?{NOTE:あんた、本気で言ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes. I am.{NOTE:はい。本木です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.08,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:いいが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.58,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I will train you as you wish.{NOTE:そんなに言うんなら、お望み通り、特訓してあげる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.46,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Let's meet in an hour.{NOTE:あたしのXXXにいらっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.89,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,This is my father's factory. Let's step in.{NOTE:これはね、父の工場なの。さ、行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Whoa.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:32.11,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,This place is secure from the wind and we can even play at night.{NOTE:ここだったら、風も当たらないし、日が暮れても大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,At night?{NOTE:日が暮れても？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.74,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.67,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You said earlier you're better\Nthan my teammates, didn't you?{NOTE:ね。あなたさっき家の部員より実力があると言ってたわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I did.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:49.46,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,That means you can do everything they do, right?{NOTE:それならあの人達に出来たことがあなたに出来ないわけないね。でしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.63,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Miss?{NOTE:お嬢様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.34,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude.{NOTE:あ。お邪魔してます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:57.01,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,But do you think you can bring the first-aid kit in here?{NOTE:あ、XXXさん、すいませんけどね、救急箱を用意してくださる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.43,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Huh? First-aid, you say?{NOTE:は？救急箱でございますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.81,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Are you hurt?\N– No.{NOTE:—え、どこがお怪我？\\N—いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.48,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.48,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,So that girl is…?{NOTE:あの方がね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:10.07,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,She's still kicking right now,\Nbut she's going to need it soon enough.{NOTE:うん。今ぴんぴんしてるけど、時期に薬が入るようになるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.15,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Let's get this going.{NOTE:さ、始めましょう。XXサーブよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.33,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:25.79,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.05,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Don't let it go!{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:30.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Got it!{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.05,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:32.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.43,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:34.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.55,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Next!\N– Ah!{NOTE:—次！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:38.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.18,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:取れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:40.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:42.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.89,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Come on!{NOTE:しっかり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:46.48,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Wow, they're amazing.{NOTE:あ、これはすごいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:48.82,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.36,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:52.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:54.70,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:55.53,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:56.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, damn it!{NOTE:あ、しまった…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あぁ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.46,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Oh dear.{NOTE:お、やった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:20.97,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.63,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I'm a little tired, how about you?{NOTE:どう？少しXX？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.17,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Shall we call it a day?{NOTE:もう勘弁してあげようか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No… no, not yet.{NOTE:いいえ。いいえ、未だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Not yet, not yet.{NOTE:まだまだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.01,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You can drop the tough act.{NOTE:やせ我慢ならおよしなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:01.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's not it.{NOTE:違います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,T-This is your special training? Don't make me laugh.{NOTE:こ、こんなものが特訓だなんて、笑っちゃうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:09.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ours was much, much more difficult.{NOTE:私たちの方がずっとずっと厳しいんだもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.73,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.82,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Let's see what you got. Accept that!{NOTE:XXXないで、受けて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.61,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:16.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:17.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.24,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:取れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:は、は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.49,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:20.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.20,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:取れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:23.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.96,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Pardon me, miss, but I think it's best to stop here.{NOTE:あの、お嬢さん…もういい加減にお止めになったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Please don't interfere.{NOTE:放っといてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.96,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Interfere? What an ungrateful kid.{NOTE:掘っとけ？可愛げのない子供はもう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.34,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—それ！\\N—あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.47,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ah!\N– There's more!{NOTE:—あぁ！\\N—未だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.73,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Don't you sleep!{NOTE:もう立って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.49,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Not yet.{NOTE:ん、未だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.24,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Not yet, not yet…{NOTE:未だ未だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.41,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:06.70,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.42,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Stand up!{NOTE:さ、立って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—あ！\\N—取れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:15.84,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{NOTE:—それ！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Kudou-san.{NOTE:工藤さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.77,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Oh no! You see, this is why I said to stop.{NOTE:あ、だからさっきで止めとけよかったんだもう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.77,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,She doesn't know when to give up.{NOTE:まったく飽きれた子だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.94,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,What madness.{NOTE:まるで気違いですよ、これじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.90,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You poor thing…{NOTE:可哀想に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.98,Default,Janitor,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.32,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You've gone through a lot, haven't you, Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:苦しんだもんね、鮎原さん。}
Comment: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:51.46,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:04.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Here comes another.{NOTE:さ、もう一度行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.39,Alternative,Kudou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Stand up. Why can't you accept such a simple ball?{NOTE:立って。あなな簡単のボールをどうして取れないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Pathetic. I'll repeat the last serve. Get ready.{NOTE:だらしがないよ。もう一度今のサービス行くわよ。良いわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:23.82,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.37,Alternative,Kudou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Come on! Fight, fight!{NOTE:頑張って。ファイト！ファイトよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.05,Alternative,Kudou,0,0,0,,It hurts…{NOTE:く、苦しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei?{NOTE:おケイ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei!{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.64,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei, come on.{NOTE:おケイ、しっかりして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.22,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Are you all right?{NOTE:大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei?{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.61,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Keep it together!{NOTE:しっかりして！おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei!{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.32,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.20,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.29,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness, you woke up!{NOTE:気がついたのね。よかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oohara-san…?{NOTE:大原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.13,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,It's all right. Don't try to move just yet.{NOTE:あ、いいのよ。未だ動かない方はいいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:どうも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.06,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,That was scary. You were reckless.{NOTE:まったく恐ろしい。無鉄砲ですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.85,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,That's not true, mister.{NOTE:そうじゃないのよ、おじさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.69,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,However, miss…{NOTE:しかしですね、お嬢さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.44,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Hey mister, did you play any sports when you were younger?{NOTE:おじさん。ね、若いこのスポーツをやったことある？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.32,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,Yes. Believe it or not, I used to play baseball.{NOTE:え。それはXXXも私はもう野球の選手だったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.65,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,I was just a spare player, though.{NOTE:あの、補欠ですけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:51.08,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,In that case, I think you'll understand Ayuhara-san's actions someday.{NOTE:それなら何時か鮎原さんの気持ちも分かる時が来ると思うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.49,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I can take it from here, mister.{NOTE:後は大丈夫。あたしに任してね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.79,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,Are you sure? All right. Please get well soon.{NOTE:そうですか？それじゃま、一つお大事に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.09,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You went through a lot, didn't you?\NAnd all by yourself, too.{NOTE:あなた自分一人で苦しんでたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.13,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I heard everything.{NOTE:聞いたわ、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:13.22,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Your request seemed strange, so I went to your school and met with professor Hongou.{NOTE:あなたの要すが変だったから、学校へ行って、本郷先生に会ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:そうですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:18.85,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,That's why I knew right away when you tried to provoke me.{NOTE:だからあなたが技とあたし起こらせるようなこと言った時ピンと来たわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.36,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I've seen right through you.{NOTE:ちゃんと分かってたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:26.99,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You blame yourself for Kudou-san's condition and want to make up for it by going through the same.{NOTE:あなたは工藤さんのことで自分を責めるあまり、工藤さんと同じ辛さを味わおうとしたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.49,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Am I right?{NOTE:違う？そうでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.74,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,There's nothing to apologize for.{NOTE:誤ることはないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:36.45,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,But what did you think it would accomplish?{NOTE:でもね、その辛さから何が生まれたって言うんでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:41.38,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, do you think it will help anyone if you bully yourself?{NOTE:鮎原さん、あなた自分を苛めて苛め抜いて、それを責任をはたしたつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.75,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you're wrong.{NOTE:だとしたら、あなたはやっぱりお間違いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.09,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You're not fit to be a captain.{NOTE:キャプテンになれる人じゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.05,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,But I guess I'm not one to talk.{NOTE:でもあたしだって人の事を言えないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:02.52,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Looking at you reminds me of my former self.{NOTE:無期に成ったあなたを見ると向かしのあたしを思い出すわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:11.66,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Just like you, I kept setting the bar higher and higher.{NOTE:あなたと同じように自分から特訓を求め続けた私。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:25.63,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Because I hate to lose,\NI always ended up very serious.{NOTE:負けず嫌いでコートを思ったらとことんやりに行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.21,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,We're the same in that regard.{NOTE:そんな性分があなたと共通知ってるのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:32.72,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:33.76,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.27,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,But I haven't always been such a volleyball addict.{NOTE:でも私は最初からバレー気違いではなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:44.27,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,The one who introduced me to volleyball was my middle school classmate.{NOTE:私をバレーに引っ張り込んだのは中学からの同級生で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.44,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Her name was Kagawa-san.{NOTE:香川さんって人だったね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:50.13,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,She was into it even more than I am now.{NOTE:だから香川さん私以上にバレーXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.61,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,No one forced us to do such intense training.{NOTE:特訓と言えば自分から進んでぶつかって行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:58.20,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,That was our choice and ours only.{NOTE:そんな部員は香川さんと私と二人ぐらいのもんだったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:07.84,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,But for some reason one day Kagawa-san refused to participate in our training.{NOTE:それがある日どうしたことか、古川さんは特訓を拒否したの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:13.72,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.89,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't go to our practice today.{NOTE:ごめんね、私今日の特訓休ませてもらうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:18.93,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.81,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san, what's wrong?{NOTE:香川さん、一体どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:27.11,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,Since I have just become captain around that time, I thought Kagawa-san was acting out of jealousy.{NOTE:丁度は私はキャプテンに成ったばかりだから、てっきり香川さんの嫌がらせだと思ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.07,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,No way.{NOTE:そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.57,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Just "because you don't feel like it"\Nis not a good reason.{NOTE:ただやりたくないでは理由に成らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.66,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,But I really don't.{NOTE:だって本当なんですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.95,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Are you sick? If that's the case, show me the medical discharge.{NOTE:病気なの？だったら診断書を見せて頂戴よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:42.33,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Or maybe you have a problem with how I run things? Then just say so.{NOTE:それとも私のやり方に不満があるなら、そう言ってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:47.46,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Haven't we been friends since middle school?{NOTE:あなたとは中学からの友達じゃないの？親友じゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.63,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san.{NOTE:香川さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:53.26,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,We're friends, right? Then please trust in me.{NOTE:ね、私達親友でしょう？だったら私の事信用して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.80,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Of course we are.{NOTE:え。それはもちろん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.85,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Then please don't ask me anything.{NOTE:だったら何も聞かないで欲しいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.89,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san.{NOTE:香川さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:05.35,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I truly thought Kagawa-san was jealous of me.{NOTE:私は香川さんに裏切られたと思った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:09.11,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,At some point, I vented my anger on the innocent underclassmen.{NOTE:そしてその怒りを罪もない後輩にぶつけたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.32,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,It's an embarrassing story…{NOTE:恥ずかしい話だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.07,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:16.99,Default,Uni student A,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:18.95,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,– Ah!\N– Next!{NOTE:—あ！\\N—次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.58,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,– Ah!\N– Come on!{NOTE:—あぁぁ！\\N—取れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.37,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.08,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.08,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.38,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You can do better.{NOTE:頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.42,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Next!{NOTE:次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.51,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.55,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,We can't take it any longer.{NOTE:もうこれ以上は入れません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.84,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,We're at our limit.{NOTE:とてもこれ以上。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.39,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Are you serious?{NOTE:何言ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.72,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,What will happen if you "can't go any longer"\Nin the middle of a game? Will you just run away?{NOTE:試合の途中でこれ以上出来ないて逃げ出すつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.77,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You have to be able to cover Kagawa-san's side.{NOTE:先輩の穴は自分で埋める。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.60,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Don't lose your spirit now.{NOTE:その決心で付いてきてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.44,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,Okay…{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:50.94,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Accept it!{NOTE:取れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.90,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Oohara-san.{NOTE:大原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.82,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何よ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.57,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,It's time to stop this.{NOTE:もう止めた方がいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:02.03,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Then get out. This team has no room for people afraid of intense training.{NOTE:引っ込んでてよ。特訓にXXお前たちの出る幕じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:06.12,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,That isn't intense training at all, that's a farce.{NOTE:いくら特訓でも、これ以上あまりにも一方XX過ぎないかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.42,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{NOTE:それどう言うこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.21,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,You're doing it only for yourself. No one benefits from it.{NOTE:だって、あなた一人で空回りしているもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.84,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Don't act like you know it all.{NOTE:偉そうな口聞かないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.17,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Everyone is in low spirits because of you.{NOTE:皆にやる気がないのはね、あなたのせいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.97,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,It's not my fault.{NOTE:あたしのせいじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:21.18,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Oohara-san, you're thinking\Nof us just as receiving machines.{NOTE:大原さん。あなたが皆のことボールを打つ機械としか考えないからなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.93,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,And what's wrong with that? You can't show your emotions during a game anyway.{NOTE:なぜ行けないの？感情に押し流された試合に勝てないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.73,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,A match is like war.{NOTE:勝負が非常よ。そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:30.27,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Aren't you the only one who thinks like that?{NOTE:その感情に流されるのはあなたではなくて？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.23,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.78,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Even machines take breaks.{NOTE:機械だって中止があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.20,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,It is captain's responsibility to know when to take those.{NOTE:その中止の波をつかんで練習させるのがキャプテンよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.95,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Shut your trap. Don't tell me things I already know.{NOTE:うるさいわね。分かり切ったこと言わないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.66,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,It's not like I expect you to become the best in a single day.{NOTE:一日貴方達にXXXされることないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.21,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Already know, you say?{NOTE:分かり切ったことかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:55.80,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,If it was so obvious to you, then you wouldn't be saying we have no spirit.{NOTE:特訓をこと会ったもの頭ごなしに入ってXXXを決めつけるあなたに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.30,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Step aside!{NOTE:そこどいてよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.76,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,It is none of your concern anymore, is it?{NOTE:貴方には関係ないでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.64,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Don't interfere with our practice.{NOTE:練習をじゃましないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.68,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,We're resuming, whether you move or not.{NOTE:動かなきゃ勝手に始めるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.10,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes!{NOTE:さ、行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.73,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– All right!\N– Let's go!{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.48,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:20.82,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:27.91,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san.{NOTE:香川さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.91,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,Why are you standing there?{NOTE:あなたはなぜそこに立ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.33,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,You're meaninglessly disturbing our practice.{NOTE:意味もなく練習のじゃまをするような。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.17,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,Why?{NOTE:あなたじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.09,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Why is she just standing there?\N– Weird.{NOTE:—XXX。\\N—ずっと変ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:42.09,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,Are you trying to show me something?{NOTE:貴方は私に何かを知らせようとしてるのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.76,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,If so, what is it?{NOTE:それは何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.39,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,What is it…?{NOTE:何だろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:48.77,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.15,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Ka…{NOTE:か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.73,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san!{NOTE:香川さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.77,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san, don't tell me…{NOTE:香川さん、あなたもしかして…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.32,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,Ah, I didn't think the ball would come so I just stood here.{NOTE:あ、ボールが来ないと思ったら、そこにいたいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.03,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Do you… can you see?{NOTE:目が…目が見えないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.03,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You can't, can you?{NOTE:見えないのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.24,Default,Uni student B,0,0,0,,Eh!?{NOTE:え？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.91,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I can still see a little bit.{NOTE:未だ少しぐらい見えるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:16.50,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I can at least tell your face from the ball.{NOTE:ボールとあなたの顔の区別ぐらいついてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:20.84,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Kagawa-san, why did you keep this from us?{NOTE:香川さん。なぜ、なぜそれを黙ってたのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.76,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I developed glaucoma.{NOTE:緑内障という病気なの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:31.18,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I realized I was losing my sight two months ago.{NOTE:目が見えなく成ると分かったのはもう二ヶ月ほど前のことなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.64,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Two months ago!?{NOTE:二ヶ月前？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.06,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,And you still continued to play volleyball?{NOTE:それなの、あなたはバレーを続けていた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:40.90,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I wanted to play as much as I could.{NOTE:出来る所までやらなくちゃ。そんな気持ちだったから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.53,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I kept silent because I didn't want you to worry about me.{NOTE:黙っていたのは同情されたくないからよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.91,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,But now you know…{NOTE:同情されいた割られてごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:51.08,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,I tried to carve our practices into my memory as much as I could, but those memories…{NOTE:折角私が目の見える家に作ろうとしたボールの思い出が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:56.38,Default,Kagawa,0,0,0,,…will disappear in no time, won't they?{NOTE:…何時でも薄められてしまうでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.67,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kagawa-san.{NOTE:ごめんなさい、香川さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.42,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I didn't know…{NOTE:知らなかったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.18,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,But that's no excuse.{NOTE:知らなかったではすまない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.22,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,And I call myself a captain?{NOTE:なぜって私はキャプテンですもの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,A captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:28.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's the captain's responsibility, isn't it.{NOTE:それがキャプテンで仕事なんですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.95,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You still need hard training.{NOTE:特訓も要るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.79,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,You need that intensity.{NOTE:扱きだって必要だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:36.87,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,But it can't just be for the captain's or coach's own satisfaction.{NOTE:でも、それは絶対にキャプテンやコーチの自己満足であってはならない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:44.17,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Whether your training does any good depends on how united your team is.{NOTE:鍛えるものと鍛えられるものの間に、心が通い合ってこそ、初めて成果が上がるんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:48.72,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Pushing forward blindly requires neither a captain nor a coach.{NOTE:ただ盲滅法至極になら、キャプテンやコーチなんて要らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.72,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Do you understand?{NOTE:分かった？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I do, Oohara-san.{NOTE:分かりました、大原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:55.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll visit Kudou-san tomorrow.{NOTE:明日になったら私工藤さんの見舞いに行きます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:08.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Up until now, I couldn't get over Kudou-san's bad performance and forgive her for collapsing.{NOTE:今まで私工藤さんにすまないと思う一方あれぐらいの練習で倒れるなんてだらしがないと思っていました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:11.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Somewhere in a corner of my mind, I blamed Kudou-san.{NOTE:心のどっか隅っこで工藤さんをXXXしていたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I blamed her weakness\Nfor me losing my title as captain.{NOTE:あんな弱虫のおかげでキャプテンを辞めさせられた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:17.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I was just thinking of myself.{NOTE:XXX。そんな考えになったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:18.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But now I understand.{NOTE:でもよく分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:22.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I lacked so much while I was their captain.{NOTE:キャプテンとして足りなかった自分ことが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oohara-san, thank you very much.{NOTE:大原さん。有難うございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:27.09,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,I'm glad you understand.{NOTE:分かってもらえて嬉しいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:30.38,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Let's hope that Kudou-san will get well soon.{NOTE:工藤さんの体が早く元通りに成ること祈ってるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:31.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:23.27,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can't lose here.{NOTE:負けちゃ行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,As soon as visiting hours start, I'll go see Kudou-san.{NOTE:面会時間に成ったら一番に工藤さんの病院へ行くのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:27.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:31.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No matter what the results are,\Na responsibility is a responsibility.{NOTE:結果はXXと責任は責任。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:40.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Even if it's hard, I can't look away.{NOTE:辛いこと、苦しいことから目をそらすなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ayuhara Kozue isn't that unreliable a person.{NOTE:我ながら、だらしなかったぞ、鮎原こずえ。}
Comment: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:55.43,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:01.02,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy members have advanced through the district qualifiers…{NOTE:地区予選の決勝を向かえた、富士見学園のメンバーは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:03.81,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,…but are still uneasy around Kozue.{NOTE:…こずえをかいていることに不安が募る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.98,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kozue is still determined to return to the club.{NOTE:おろしも、こずえはバレー部に戻ろうと決意していた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:10.53,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, her resolve breaks down under coach Hongou's words.{NOTE:だが、その決心も本郷の言葉に打ち砕かれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:13.99,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,"We can win even without Ayuhara", says Hongou.{NOTE:鮎原がいなくても勝てると本郷は言う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.99,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Does she really not have a place in the volleyball club after all?{NOTE:もはや自分はバレー部にはようのない人間なのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:19.29,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kozue breaks into tears…{NOTE:絶望に泣き崩れるこずえだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:23.04,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
